<p>Located in the centre of Valletta, the hotel is a former palazzo and the restoration is amazing. From the striking entrance, the elegant reception, the restaurant â€“ which is out of this world - to the rooms, the attention to detail and the gorgeous colours are just so so stylish.</p>

<p><img src="/images/malta/rosselli/rosselli-1-w1200.jpg" alt="rosselli-1-w1200.jpg" /></p>

<p>The colours are soft and muted to contrast with the bold wall coverings and make you think of secret gardens. Despite the hotel only having six rooms, the space and light create a feeling tranquillity and ease. Malta is looking for 6* tourists and you certainly feel like one at <a href="https://rossellimalta.com/" target="_blank">Rosselli</a>.</p>

<p><img src="/images/malta/rosselli/rosselli-9-w1200.jpg" alt="rosselli-9-w1200.jpg" /></p>

<p>Some rooms have a private spa, sauna and rain shower. With Lâ€™Occitane toiletries, sumptuous monogramed towels, complimentary tea, coffee and wine in your room as well as everything else you would expect from an AX hotel you could happily just stay in!</p>

